map_npcs.name: Explorer Dave
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, hey there, you trapped down here too buddy?
The cave back here houses some sort of weird machine.
It looks like it's missing a component though.
I'll do some searching myself, here's a map of what I've found so far! Stay safe!

map_npcs.name: Seer Sister Laurel
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Though the path has been treacherous, you've made it this far.
Return to Thunder Peak. There, we shall await your challenge.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
I am one of the Seer Sisters.
This lake is rather calming isn't it?
I shall test your skill.

map_npcs.name: Uncertain Researcher
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Those things... I don't know what they did to the rest of the team...
They even have the Data Disk I'd need to start up the teleporter system...
I'm as good as trapped now...
*sigh...*

map_npcs.name: Rival Cade
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Come back if you find that missing piece.
I'll, uh, keep watch...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hey, {player}, Al told me this hunk of junk is supposed to get us back to the surface.
I've patched it up, but it looks like it's still missing a component...

map_npcs.name: CHANGE THIS YA DINGUS
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Go ahead and insert the disk to the slot on the machine.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Well it's about time!
What was I going to do if you died out there?
Go ahead and insert the disk to the slot on the machine.
